Package bowling.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdditionalRoll
    This class defines the additional roll a player can have in the 10th frame.
    FirstRoll
    This class represents the first roll for a frame.
    Frame
    This represents each frame for a single player.
    Line
    Class that represents a line of 10 frames for a single player.
    Roll
    This class will model a single Roll for a player.
    SecondRoll
    Class that identifies the second roll for a frame.
    SpecialFrame
    This class represents the 10th frame if it becomes an special frame like when the player has a third shot.
